- "basking in the glow of a high-performing sun" is a metaphorical expression indicating sectors with high performance;
- "average metric value shining brighter than the threshold of 80" refers to sectors having an average performance metric value above 80;
- "2023" is the specific year for which the performance metrics are evaluated.

sql:
SELECT company_name
FROM companies
WHERE industry = (SELECT industry FROM companies WHERE industry = 'Technology' LIMIT 1);
